{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "悟空从三藏口中得知美猴王本是\\n善良的魔兽，但因遭到人类背叛而被封印。\\n美猴王对人类的复仇之心正是因此而起。\\n为了化解他对人类的仇恨，悟空解开了\\n美猴王的封印并和王子等人联手与其对战！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "虽然我们斗志昂扬地\\n来到了紧箍这里……\\n但这个封印，要怎么解除啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "什么？重要的紧箍封印步骤\\n你竟然没有留意吗！？\\n只知道战斗的武痴就是靠不住……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "稍等一下。\\n只要采取相反的步骤，\\n应该就能解除封印。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "那家伙……仙宝的秘密研究多了，\\n都能当封印师了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "久等了。封印基本已经解除……\\n接下来不知道会变成什么样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "这么快就出现魔兽了啊……\\n不过这也在意料之中。\\n美猴王也快苏醒了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "是啊，趁他醒来之前\\n先把魔兽都消灭了吧。\\n要耗光美猴王的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "师父！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "嗯？悟空……\\n怎么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "能告诉俺美猴王为什么\\n那么憎恨人类吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "听他的口气……\\n好像并不只是因为\\n他是魔兽吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "悟空……好吧。\\n现在一切都结束了，\\n我就告诉你吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "美猴王——据说他\\n原本是不会攻击人类的\\n温顺魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "古代麒麟族里似乎\\n也有不少和他接触过的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "啊！那他果然\\n是善良的魔兽吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "是的。他是非常稀有的例子。\\n也许可以说是一个变异种。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "然而……不幸的是，无论他的意愿如何，\\n他的力量都会制造魔兽。\\n而那魔兽会不断杀害人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "渐渐地，和他有接触的麒麟族\\n也开始忌讳并远离他。\\n而到了最后……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "面临人类灭亡\\n与封印美猴王的抉择时，\\n没有一个人出面保护他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "他被人类抛弃，\\n并被孤零零地\\n封印在了紧箍里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "孤零零地……在紧箍里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "哪怕只有一次也好，我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "怎么了，悟空？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "俺想起来了……\\n俺果然是认得他的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "之前俺对紧箍恶作剧，\\n被紧箍之力吞噬的时候……\\n俺听到了他的声音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "他一直在说\\n“哪怕只有一次也好——\\n我想与某个人相伴”……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "美猴王竟然说过那种话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "师父……俺果然还是……\\n想和美猴王一起活下去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "你又在说胡话了……\\n我从来没听说过有哪个人类\\n能与魔兽共存。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "那俺呢？俺又算什么！？\\n人类也能成为封印师这件事，\\n除了师父以外没有人相信俺。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "即便是这样，俺也做到了。\\n就像师父相信俺那样，\\n俺成了封印师！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "修行很艰苦，\\n但是俺坚持下来了。\\n这都是多亏了师父相信俺。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "所以俺也想像那样\\n去相信美猴王！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "……\\n呵呵，之前明明还只是个\\n小孩子而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "什么时候都会说\\n这么撼动人心的话了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "悟空，\\n不封印美猴王的办法……\\n倒也不是没有。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "诶！？真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "嗯。但是，那非常危险。\\n无法保证你的安全。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "俺已经做好觉悟了。\\n因为他……\\n是俺的朋友！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "啊……这真是出乎意料啊。\\n魔兽太多了，没完没了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "是啊，真是的……\\n想出这种战术的大蠢蛋\\n到底是谁啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "是我！但你不也参与了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "八戒！悟净！\\n紧箍已经被封印了，\\n为什么还会有魔兽！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "噢，是你们啊。\\n对不住啊！\\n我们解除了封印。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "什么！？\\n都不和三藏商量一下，\\n这是在做什么啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "你们好啊。怎么？\\n想来喂魔兽了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110322_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "八戒",
            "context": "不。有人想和你谈谈，\\n你就陪他一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "你说……谈谈？\\n哈……人类真是无论过去\\n还是现在……都这么无趣呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "古代麒麟族里，\\n也有像你们一样\\n试图与我和谐相处的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "但是啊……当魔兽破坏了城市，\\n一切都变了。他们毫不犹豫地\\n改变主意封印了我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "那时我就发誓……\\n下次醒来的时候一定要让你们\\n见识到可怕的灭亡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "美猴王！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "是悟空啊……让你也见识一下吧。\\n迄今为止在紧箍里不断燃烧的\\n这股黑暗之力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "美猴王……俺会阻止你的。\\n所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "悟净！\\n把你藏在怀里的紧箍给俺！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110323_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟净",
            "context": "呃……被你发现了！？\\n真没办法。给你吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120185_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "美猴王",
            "context": "哈，又要用紧箍把我封印起来吗？\\n就凭你这个半吊子？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110324_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悟空",
            "context": "不……不是的。\\n俺是要这么做！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "戴上了紧箍！？\\n悟空，你要做什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "那就是悟空的觉悟。\\n他选择相信美猴王\\n而做出的决定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "他是打算……通过紧箍，\\n用自己的意志和力量\\n将美猴王封印起来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "如果成功了，\\n美猴王就不必\\n被紧箍的封印所束缚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110299_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三藏",
            "context": "不过这是一个危险的赌注。\\n万一失败，他可能就没命了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20410_07_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "什么！你竟然答应他\\n去做那么危险的事？",
